data.description: Welcome to this well taken care of 3 bedroom, 2-story home in beautiful Mesquite, NV! Features include a 2 car garage, tall ceiling fans throughout, and a spacious backyard with synthetic grass, a putting green, and a Jacuzzi Hot Tub. The home is thoughtfully upgraded with large ceiling fans, beautiful fixtures, flooring and more. Located in the gated community of Copper Bluffs, the home sits on a larger corner lot and the neighborhood even includes an exercise room!
